Name: Yolo Space Hacker
About the game: Join the Y0L0 Space Hacker Agency, an ethical hacker organisation. Your first mission: hack into a space station and unravel its mystery. What Happened On Bikini-72? - Explore a 3d Adventure Game - Solve puzzles based on real security breaches - Crack passwords - Intercept and temper with web requests - Get passed servers security - All of this in a secure environment to learn and improve your skills Real hacking tools Use the hacker tools integrated into the game: a terminal, a web proxy, nmap to scan the network, dirb for brute-force attacks on websites, password lists to force authentication, John to crack passwords, reverse shells, privilege escalation techniques... Once the flaw is found, run a Reverse Shell and get Admin. Where to start? - You know nothing about cybersecurity? That's fine, we're set to tell you everything you need to know! We have prepared a comprehensive Cyber-security tutorial for beginners. Complete missions, to learn step by step the various techniques used by hackers. You'll probably have to use your brain a little bit, but you'll never get stuck. - You already know the basics of Linux machines and a bit of programming? That's great, it's going to get really interesting!
